### Gateway服务测试请求

### 1. 测试未认证访问（应返回401）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/order/test
Accept: application/json

### 2. 测试用户登录（白名单，应成功）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user001",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. 测试商家登录（白名单，应成功）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/seller/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "merchant001",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4. 测试用户注册（白名单）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "phone": "13800138001"
}

### 5. 测试携带Token访问（登录后替换satoken值）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/auth/info
satoken: ec00bd94-60cd-4a2c-8676-8064673c0a37
Accept: application/json

### 6. 测试IP限流（快速发送多次，第31次应返回429）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/auth/login
Accept: application/json

### 7. 测试路由转发到商品服务
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/product/all
satoken: ae6daac2-2a7c-4a29-98b9-a61ea84c9dab
Accept: application/json

### 8. 测试商家端路由
GET http://localhost:8080/api/seller/product/all
satoken: a70fb379-6496-4211-9ac2-ee52ed909a93
Accept: application/json
